Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,南方女王前情提要\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Previously on Queen of the South...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.46,0:00:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得迈阿密怎么样\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}How do you feel about Miami?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.02,0:00:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么可不喜欢的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What's not to like?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.29,0:00:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你来管理\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I would like you to run it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.64,0:00:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,勒内就像是我的儿子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}René was like a son to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,无论是谁干的都会付出代价\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Whoever did this will pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,艾米莉亚不在这里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Emilia's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但我知道哪里能找到她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But I know where to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,有些话我不能说\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I can't be honest with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有些事你不了解\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}There are things that you don't know and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能再见你了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and I can't see you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.86,0:00:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是这么想的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You don't mean this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,法官今天来我的办公室了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Judge came by my office today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,特蕾莎 他想要你死\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Teresa, he wants you dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想告诉你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I just want you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我全力支持你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm all in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.48,0:00:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,拉斐特杀了托尼\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Lafayette killed Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.93,0:00:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,请节哀顺变 特蕾莎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm so sorry for your loss, Teresa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.77,0:01:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是埃利亚斯吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Was it Elias?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.05,0:01:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.03,0:01:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是一个本地问题 我正在处理\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's a local matter that I'm handling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.02,0:01:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,现在佛罗里达南部已经稳定了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Now that South Florida is secured,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.45,0:01:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让你把我介绍给你在纽约的表哥 科斯佳\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I would like you to introduce me to your cousin Kostya, in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.48,0:01:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯佳是个非常谨慎的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Kostya is a very cautious man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.09,0:01:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他很少和人亲自见面\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's rare that he meets somebody face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.96,0:01:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他不信任他圈子外面的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He doesn't trust people outside his circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.23,0:01:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.22,0:01:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你不明白 特蕾莎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I do not think you do, Teresa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果科斯佳突然来拜访你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If Kostya pays you a surprise visit...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.58,0:01:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他会是你这辈子最后见到的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He's the last person you will ever see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.21,0:01:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,请安排吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Set it up, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.51,0:01:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:01:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,无意冒犯 暴龙\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Respectfully, T. rex,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.06,0:01:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们刚拿下迈阿密\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}we just took over Miami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:01:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,波阿斯还在稳定局面\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Boaz's still working out the kinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.25,0:01:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在那还没有站稳脚跟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We're on shaky ground there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:02:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这么着急和俄国人交易\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Why move so fast with the Russians?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,声势\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Momentum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们把科斯佳发展为合作伙伴\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If we expand with Kostya as our partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,别人会认为我们实力强大\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}we will be seen as strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,有哈维尔的消息吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Have we heard from Javier?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他在了结一些事情\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He's tying some loose ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就在前面几英里的地方\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's just a couple more miles ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你是她唯一想找的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're the only person she wanted to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,兰德尔拽她下车之前她还想给你打电话\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}She tried to call you just before Randall pulled her from the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是兰德尔杀了她吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It was Randall who killed her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的脏活都是他做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Does all the dirty work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为什么抓走艾米莉亚\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Why did they take Emilia?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我表哥勒内被谋杀了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}My cousin René was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他们认为她与这件事有关\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}They thought that she had something to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个善良的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}She was a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,她和这事一点关系都没有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}She had nothing to do with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,无论你想对他做什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Whatever you wanna do to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,都是他活该\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He deserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到我儿子了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Did you find my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,还没有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.36,0:03:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,刚路过门多萨的酒吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Went by Mendoza's bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她雇佣了大批人马\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}She's hired herself an army.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,除非把他们全干掉 否则不可能悄悄接近她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No quiet way to get to her unless we bring 'em all in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,门多萨很清楚该怎么保护自己\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Mendoza's smart enough to cover her ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也不知道她有我们什么把柄\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And we have no idea what she's got on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不必要的时候先不要激怒她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Let's not poke the bear until we have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.04,0:03:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有必要 也不用我们自己动手\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And when we do, we'll keep our hands clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,马塞尔会把事办了 她想不到他会出手\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Marcel will get the job done. She won't see him coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个想法也许能让我们获得一些优势\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I did come across something that might give us an edge on Mendoza.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来她找了个新的生意伙伴\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Looks like she's got herself a new business partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:03:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是个女人 有两个保镖\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Woman, two heavies...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,之前从没见过她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}never seen her before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,有意思\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,去认识一下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Get acquainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,让她见识见识我们南方人的魅力\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Show her some of our southern charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,乐意之至\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Happy to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你想为你的教子报仇雪恨\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I know you want payback for your godson's murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但我只是想确认\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but I just wanna make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.51,0:04:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有被仇恨冲昏头脑\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that darkness isn't blinding you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-你改变主意了吗  -没有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Have you changed your mind? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但一旦我们这么做了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But once we do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就不能再回头了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}there's no going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,特蕾莎 我们都是道上混的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Teresa, we're all in this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的手上都沾满了鲜血\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We all got blood on our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.25,0:04:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你杀了鲍比\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You killed Bobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我杀了伯迪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I took Birdie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经不计前嫌了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You and I got past that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,或许你和法官也可以这样\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Maybe you can do the same thing with the Judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他控制着我们已经太长时间了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He's kept us under his thumb for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经受够了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm done with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你想怎么做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}How you wanna do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,拉斐特很腐败 但他还是个法官\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Lafayette's dirty, but he's still a judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说他能派执法机关来对付我们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That means he can bring law enforcement down on our heads,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我说的不只是本地执法部门\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and I'm not just talking local law enforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦调查局 缉毒局\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Feds, DEA...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以把他的死亡伪装成他自己犯罪的结果\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We can make his death look like a result of his own crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉全世界拉斐特的真实面目\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Show the world who Lafayette really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,一个腐败的杀人犯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}a corrupt killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦他被曝光\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Once he's exposed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,受他控制的那些警察和政客\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}the cops and politicians in his pocket
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就不会冒险调查他的死亡\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}won't risk investigating his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那就开始吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Let's get on with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个好计划 特蕾西塔\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's a good plan, Teresita.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(184,286)}我们在他偷腥的时候下手\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We catch the Judge with his pants down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(170,286)}他永远想不到我们会来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He'll never see us coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(140,286)}他似乎一直都能领先我们一步\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He always seems to be a step ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(154,286)}这一次不能再这样了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This time, he can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(144,286)}我们需要谈谈乔治的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We need to talk about George.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他很愤怒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He's angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得我们在伯迪的事上放过了杜马斯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Thinks we let Dumas off the hook for Birdie's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在不能有任何不稳定因素\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We cannot have any loose cannons right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(174,286)}袭击法官已经足够危险了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The hit on the Judge is dangerous enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我会找他谈谈\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们应该让波阿斯从迈阿密派来一些增援\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Maybe we should ask Boaz to send some backup from Miami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No.
