Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,蟑螂会藏在黑暗的地方\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Roaches run from the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.66,0:16:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 虽然看起来不怎么样\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Okay, well, it isn't much to look at,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但我觉得这就是重点\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but I figured that's kinda the point...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,藏在显眼的地方\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}hide in plain sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-这里非常合适  -太好了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- It's perfect. - Great, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.24,0:16:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我租下了所有房间\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, I rented out all the rooms
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,所有这里不会有闲杂人员\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}so you won't have any lookie-loos,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你要梳洗一下 你的行李都在12号房间\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and your stuff is in room number 12 if you need to freshen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我送你过去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 凯莉·安妮\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Listen, Kelly Anne.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.79,0:16:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这场和拉斐特的战争\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This war with Lafayette...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,非常严峻\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}it's really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:17:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让你去城外和奇乔的母亲待在一起\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I would like you to go and stay with Chicho's mom in Uptown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我哪也不去 我的家就在这\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm not going anywhere. This is my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I know it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但特蕾莎需要你帮她打理生意\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But Teresa needs your help with the business,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不是冲锋陷阵\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}not with a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.14,0:17:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你要注意安全 听到了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You be safe, you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我会的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪了 混蛋\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Where you been, cabrón?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.18,0:17:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(192,275)\fs18\bord1.5\shad0\fn方正黑体_GBK\b1}我要和特蕾莎谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(192,275)\fs18\bord1.5\shad0\fn方正黑体_GBK\b1}马上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道法官为什么想要杀了你 老板\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I know why the Judge tried to kill you, patrona.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,快说\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Better start talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我杀了勒内\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I killed René...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,法官的侄子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The Judge's nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在酒吧卫生间打了起来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We got into a fight in the bathroom at the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,把尸体藏在了他车的后备箱里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Hid his body in the trunk of his car...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,放火烧了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Set it on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,兰德尔查到了一些证据\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Randall found some evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他抓走了艾米莉亚\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He took Emilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.99,0:18:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,她一定为了保护我撒了谎 老板\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}She must have lied to protect me, patrona.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I think
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,她告诉他是你下令袭击勒内\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}she told him you ordered the hit on René.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他们杀了她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And they killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(192,275)\fs18\bord1.5\shad0\fn方正黑体_GBK\b1}原谅我 老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.73,0:18:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你害死了托尼 你差点害死特蕾莎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You got Tony killed! You almost got Teresa killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你死定了 混蛋\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Now you will die, cabrón!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.52,0:18:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,别让这个王八蛋离开你的视线\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Don't let this hijo de puta out of your sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哈维尔救过我的命\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Javier saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他冒着生命危险想要保护我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He risked his own trying to protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他和詹姆斯一样勇敢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He's been as courageous as James.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但他当面骗了你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But he lied to your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯也是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And so did James.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他也不完全是个圣人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He wasn't exactly a saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.47,0:19:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,至少哈维尔 他撒谎是为了保护心爱的女人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}At least Javier... he lied to protect the woman he loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我让你盯着他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I told you not to leave him alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.77,0:19:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,哈维不会逃跑 他是个集团士兵\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Javi ain't running. He's a cartel soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道自己违背了老板的命令 而且还欺骗了她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He knows he disobeyed the boss' orders and lied to her to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,无论你如何决定 他都会接受\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Look, he's good with whatever you decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We'll need him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,拉斐特正在找我们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Lafayette is coming for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,更不用说波阿斯管理着迈阿密\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Not to mention Boaz runs Miami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了他表弟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Killing his cousin...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那会让他发疯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that's gonna set his hair on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,先让他活着\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}For now, he lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,杜马斯说得对\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Dumas was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该跟法官和解\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I should make peace with the Judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,门多萨小姐 真巧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Ms. Mendoza, what a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.10,0:20:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我正想着你呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You were just on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你认为我下令杀了你侄子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I know you think I ordered your nephew's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我的一个手下刚承认了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}One of my men just confessed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在我的酒吧和勒内争吵时杀了他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}to killing René in a fight at my bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.25,0:20:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该知道我不能接受这种解释\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You'll forgive me if I find that hard to swallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你企图杀了我 还杀了我的教子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You tried to kill me and killed my godson.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.01,0:20:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都失去了家人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Both of us lost family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我想找个办法让我们摒弃前嫌\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I would like to try to find a way to put this behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意改善我们之间的关系\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm open to mending fences
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你把你的人交给我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}once you hand your man over to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这我不能同意\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I won't allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾经纵容过你 门多萨小姐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I've indulged you, Ms. Mendoza.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我让你和你组织里的人渣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I've let you and all the riffraff in your organization
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:20:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在我的城市里闲晃 好像你们属于这里似的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}walk around my city like you belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来对我仁慈的回报\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And it appears my reward for not showing you my teeth
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你忘记了自己的位置 小姑娘\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}is you forgetting your place, little lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, let me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不把你的人交给我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If you don't hand over your man,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.82,0:21:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我就把你的人头交给你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I will hand you your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会回应威胁\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I don't respond to threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.34,0:21:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是威胁\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's not a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.69,0:21:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这是承诺\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,特蕾西塔\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Teresita,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉法官的都是真的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}what you told the Judge is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.07,0:21:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,无论哈维尔是死是活\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Whether Javier lives or dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.03,0:21:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,都由你决定\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}it's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你想怎么办 特蕾西塔\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What do you wanna do, Teresita?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我满足了拉斐特所有的要求\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I've done everything Lafayette demanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.00,0:21:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经给了他很多钱\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I've paid him a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我继续妥协\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If I do this now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,会是什么结果\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}where does it end?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在知道你在追杀他了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He knows you're after him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他会不断地袭击我们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He'll just keep hitting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.88,0:21:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们就更猛烈的反击\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Then we'll hit him harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.02,0:21:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那就意味着要袭击警察\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That means hitting cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:21:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,腐败的警察 杀人的强盗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Dirty cops. Murderous thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.60,0:21:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.76,0:22:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们是他的私人军队\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But they're his own private army.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.78,0:22:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他控制着这座城市\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He runs this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.03,0:22:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,即便我们赢了 我们也会损失惨重\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Even if we win, we're gonna lose a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.23,0:22:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会失去更多\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}They'll lose more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.15,0:22:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,老板\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Patrona.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这座城市是我们的私人伊甸园 马塞尔\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This city has been our private Eden, Marcel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.99,0:22:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,门多萨\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Mendoza...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.83,0:22:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是外来物种\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}...is an invasive species.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,她正在这里生根发芽\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}She's putting down roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.24,0:23:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你想把她除掉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You wanna cut her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.83,0:23:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你的答案\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I need your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.85,0:23:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是站在我这边\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Are you with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.33,0:23:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我对你更加熟悉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're the devil I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.18,0:23:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道她在哪吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You know where she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.14,0:23:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.50,0:23:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,她和她的人藏在一个安全地点\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}She's holed up with her people at a safe location.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.77,0:23:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,塞德里克和我的人正在盯着她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Cedric and my crew... they're sitting on her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-他们会协助你的人  -不用 兰德尔能搞定\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- They'll help your boys out. - No, Randall can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.60,0:23:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不 很抱歉 法官\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No. I'm sorry, Judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.11,0:23:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这次我不能冒任何风险\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm not taking any chances this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.88,0:23:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我的人会确保对门多萨的袭击万无一失\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}My boys'll make sure that nothing goes wrong with the hit on Mendoza.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.42,0:23:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这场战争今天就会结束\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This war ends today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.18,0:24:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我侦查过了 特蕾莎·门多萨就在这\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I did the recon. Teresa Mendoza's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.77,0:24:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,她有多少人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}How many men are with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.44,0:24:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,四个 这个地方是孤立的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Four. The place is isolated.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.77,0:24:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,进出只有一条路\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Only one way in or out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.77,0:24:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-所以我们把他们困住了  -而且人数占优\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- So we got 'em boxed in... - And outnumbered.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.82,0:24:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就像瓮中捉鳖 兄弟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Like shooting fish in a barrel, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.78,0:24:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,现在先不要得意忘形\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Let's not start stroking each other just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.88,0:24:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的人集合起来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Get your boys together.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.61,0:25:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,撤退 撤退\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Fall back! Fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.13,0:25:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,杜马斯背叛了我们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Dumas set us up!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.66,0:25:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他要逃跑\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He's running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.71,0:26:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊 混蛋\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Acá, cabrón!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.44,0:26:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把他们都干掉了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Hey, we get 'em all?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.15,0:26:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.68,0:26:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你搞什么 兄弟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What the hell, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.92,0:26:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要杀了伯迪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Why'd you do Birdie that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.22,0:26:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,伯迪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Birdie?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.86,0:26:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是在服从命令 兄弟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I was just following orders, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.99,0:27:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个士兵 和你一样 好吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm a soldier, same as you. 'Kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.33,0:27:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个平民\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}She was a civilian.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.56,0:27:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.78,0:27:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那确实很糟糕\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It was messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.29,0:27:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果你这么做了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}See, but you do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.67,0:27:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一切又都重新开始了 好吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}it all starts up again. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.69,0:28:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是拉斐特\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's Lafayette.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.32,0:28:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你是一个警察杀手了 门多萨小姐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So now you're a cop killer, Ms. Mendoza.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.30,0:28:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那些人不是警察\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Those men weren't cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.59,0:28:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前见识到了低估你会有多么危险\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I learned early on how dangerous it is to underestimate you, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.08,0:28:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我给自己买了一小份保险\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So I bought myself a little insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.78,0:28:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我 你最近和你的俄罗斯朋友谈过话吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Do tell me. Have you spoken to your Russian friend lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.72,0:28:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,打个招呼 亲爱的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Say hello, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.02,0:28:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 特蕾莎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Hello, Teresa.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.67,0:28:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在酒店把我抓走了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}They grabbed me from my hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.18,0:28:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他的警察杀了两个我的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}His cop shot two of my men.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.02,0:28:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白现在的情况了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Is the picture becoming clear now?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.54,0:28:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道她和什么人有关系吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Do you know who she's connected to?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.34,0:28:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常清楚\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Oh, I have a pretty good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.83,0:29:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会找到你 然后杀了你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}They will hunt you down and kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.96,0:29:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不会在乎你是谁\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}They don't care who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.69,0:29:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那时你也会陪在我身边 亲爱的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And you'll be right there beside me, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.43,0:29:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会同归于尽\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Mutually-assured destruction...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.03,0:29:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你把杀死我侄子的凶手交给我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}unless you give me my nephew's killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.21,0:29:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我要在午夜之前收到回复\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I expect an answer by midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.42,0:29:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,老板\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Patrona.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.64,0:29:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道该怎么做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You know what you have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.87,0:29:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Está bien.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.90,0:29:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,本来不会变成这样\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It didn't have to be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.47,0:29:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你相信我 我本来可以保护你 但现在不能了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If you trusted me, I could've protected you, but now I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.74,0:30:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,和你一起共事 老板\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Working with you, patrona...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.75,0:30:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(192,275)\fs18\bord1.5\shad0\fn方正黑体_GBK\b1}是很棒的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.83,0:30:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我欠你的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I owe that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.49,0:30:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,干杯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Salud.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.37,0:30:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.89,0:30:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们进来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Let them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.43,0:30:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都不要动\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Everybody just breathe easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.19,0:30:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,把手伸出来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Hands where I can see 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.40,0:31:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是以警察身份来的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're not here as the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.36,0:31:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我来的目的 门多萨女士\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You know why I'm here, Ms. Mendoza.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.73,0:31:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,让这一切都结束吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Let's put an end to all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.17,0:31:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(192,275)\fs18\bord1.5\shad0\fn方正黑体_GBK\b1}保重 兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.66,0:31:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,来世再见 兄弟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll see you on the other side, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.61,0:31:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我是对的 老板\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I was right, patrona.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.11,0:31:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,认为在这种生活中可以拥有不同的东西 我们确实是疯了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We were crazy to think we would have something different in this life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.21,0:31:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(192,275)\fs18\bord1.5\shad0\fn方正黑体_GBK\b1}照顾好她
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.21,0:31:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(192,275)\fs18\bord1.5\shad0\fn方正黑体_GBK\b1}永远都会
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.30,0:32:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.06,0:32:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.59,0:32:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.66,0:32:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,戴维斯 你让我担心死了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Davis, you had me worried sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.77,0:32:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟踪我的手机\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You tracked my phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.43,0:32:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你很愤怒 但我原谅你了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I know you're angry, but I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.88,0:32:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以回家了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You can come back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.90,0:32:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你原谅我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.62,0:32:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你违抗了我 戴维斯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You defied me, Davis,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.73,0:32:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但你展现出了出乎我意料的毅力\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but you showed fortitude I didn't know you had.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.56,0:32:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这给了我希望\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It gives me hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.67,0:32:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,什么希望\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Hope for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.80,0:33:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你比我想象得更加像我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That you're more like me than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.54,0:33:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-去死吧  -法官\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Go to hell. - Judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.10,0:33:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要解决这件事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We need to wrap this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.06,0:33:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你被骗了 孩子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You were tricked, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.38,0:33:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,门多萨的手下 就是你泄露消息的那个人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Mendoza's man, the one you confided in...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.30,0:33:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是杀害你表哥的凶手\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}he's the man who murdered your cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.75,0:33:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你撒谎 你什么话都说得出来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're lying. You'd say anything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.40,0:33:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,门多萨亲自把他交给了我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Mendoza handed him over to me herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.06,0:33:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是他害死了那个可爱的姑娘\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He's the reason that sweet girl died.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.87,0:33:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不用担心\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.10,0:33:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他会得到应有的下场\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He gonna get what's coming to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.39,0:34:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 傻逼\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Let's do this, pendejo.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.09,0:34:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他说什么 兰德尔\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What's he saying, Randall?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.84,0:34:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他说“来吧 傻逼”\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He's saying, "Let's do this, pendejo."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.88,0:34:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,必须敬佩一个坦然面对死亡的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Gotta admire a man who welcomes his own firing squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.03,0:34:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,对事不对人 朋友\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Nothing personal, amigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.20,0:34:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我其实还有点欣赏你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I actually kinda liked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.81,0:34:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,兰德尔\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Randall!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.19,0:35:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,梅泰里发生的枪战导致六名授勋警官牺牲\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The shoot-out in Metairie took the lives of six decorated officers,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.23,0:35:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,包括反黑突击队的领导人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}including the head of the anti-gang strike team,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.17,0:35:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,警探兰德尔·格林\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Detective Randall Green.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.94,0:35:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,警方目前把此事定性为涉黑暴力冲突\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Police at this time are calling it a gang-related incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.77,0:35:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,兰德尔死了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Randall is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.18,0:35:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,哈维尔\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Javier.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.16,0:35:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他战斗到了最后一刻\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He fought to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.97,0:35:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉把你牵扯进来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm sorry you were pulled into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.42,0:35:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这让你付出了多大的代价\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I know how much this has cost you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.13,0:35:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不要觉得我是忘恩负义的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Do not think I am ungrateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.20,0:35:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(192,275)\fs18\bord1.5\shad0\fn方正黑体_GBK\b1}你好 我是奥克萨娜
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.78,0:35:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(192,275)\fs18\bord1.5\shad0\fn方正黑体_GBK\b1}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.24,0:35:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(192,275)\fs18\bord1.5\shad0\fn方正黑体_GBK\b1}不不不 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.68,0:36:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(192,275)\fs18\bord1.5\shad0\fn方正黑体_GBK\b1}一切顺利 她干得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.66,0:36:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(192,275)\fs18\bord1.5\shad0\fn方正黑体_GBK\b1}当然
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.04,0:36:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(192,275)\fs18\bord1.5\shad0\fn方正黑体_GBK\b1}我会告诉她的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.53,0:36:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好消息是你引起了他的注意\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The good news is that you have his attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.95,0:36:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,坏消息是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The bad news...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.22,0:36:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你引起了他的注意\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}is that you have his attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.65,0:36:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们要和科斯佳做生意了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So we are in business with Kostya?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.41,0:36:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.08,0:36:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不知是福还是祸\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}For better or for worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.07,0:36:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.01,0:36:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,法官倒下了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The Judge is down,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.03,0:36:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但他还没有出局\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but he's not out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.42,0:36:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,只要他还活着\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}As long as he's breathing,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.46,0:36:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他就会是我们的麻烦\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}he's gonna be a problem for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.50,0:36:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他失去了权力\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If he loses his power,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.14,0:36:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他就只是一个普通人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}he's just a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.24,0:36:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,任何人都可以被杀死\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Any man can be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.21,0:37:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Dave?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.21,0:37:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}My son.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.93,0:37:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Son?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.24,0:37:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Son?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.76,0:37:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝啊 我干了什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}God. What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.46,0:38:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,塔扎说菲尼克斯来了个新治安官\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Taza said there's a new sheriff in Phoenix
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.42,0:38:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,正在清理腐败\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that's cleaning up corruption,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.74,0:38:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他需要更多行贿资金\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}so he's gonna need more money for bribes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.48,0:38:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-批准吧  -好的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Send it. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.01,0:38:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,迈阿密怎么样了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}How's Miami?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.17,0:38:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不太顺利\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's a little bumpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.13,0:38:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,波阿斯不得不除掉几个找麻烦的贩子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Boaz had to dispose of a few dealers that were causing problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.04,0:38:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在那多留些人是明智之举\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You were smart to keep extra men there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.20,0:38:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,新的经理人呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What about the new bankers?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.59,0:38:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我还在检查推荐信\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm still checking references,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.92,0:38:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但我列了一份用来洗钱的新生意名单\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but I did make a list of new businesses to clean our money,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.22,0:38:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我也在留意对滨水房产和一些商业地产\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and I'm looking into making an investment on the waterfront property
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.20,0:38:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,进行投资的机会\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}as well as some commercial real estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.95,0:38:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.46,0:38:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.01,0:38:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,乐意帮忙\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Happy to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.59,0:38:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去开会了 但这套西装太酷了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm gonna get to that meeting, but that suit is baller.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.76,0:38:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.85,0:38:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 路易斯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's okay, Luis.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.79,0:39:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说你酒吧前发生了爆炸\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I heard there was an explosion in front of your bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.86,0:39:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.95,0:39:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 谢谢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.29,0:39:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.75,0:39:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说你进了医院\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}they said you were in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.04,0:39:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来要过去的 但是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I was gonna come, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.34,0:39:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定你想不想让我去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I wasn't sure you'd want me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.21,0:39:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴你没有去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm glad you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.19,0:39:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,过去一个月\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I spent the last month
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.73,0:39:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我都在思考我们之间\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}putting all the pieces together of what went down
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.36,0:39:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}between you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.85,0:39:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你不只是个\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I know you're not just a
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.67,0:39:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,酒吧老板或是龙舌兰经销商\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}bar owner or a tequila distributor.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.78,0:39:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我真相\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.71,0:39:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我掌管一个贩毒集团\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I run a drug cartel.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.76,0:39:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的是真的吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.53,0:40:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我在一起的每一分钟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Every minute you spend with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.43,0:40:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,都充满了危险\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.20,0:40:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你离开\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I need you to go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.70,0:40:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不要再回来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Don't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.25,0:40:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你骗了我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.62,0:40:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.41,0:40:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,其他所有的一切\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Everything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.15,0:40:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,也都是谎言吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}was it a lie too?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.98,0:40:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.83,0:40:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,菲尼克斯 亚特兰大 迈阿密\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Phoenix, Atlanta, Miami.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.61,0:40:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还有纽约\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Now, New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.30,0:41:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们三个月就把生意扩大了一倍\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We doubled our operation in three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.90,0:41:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,要注意的事太多了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That's a lot to keep an eye on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.55,0:41:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没有风险 就没有回报\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Ain't no risk it, no biscuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.46,0:41:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你要留下吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.42,0:41:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我会待在这的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'ma stick around.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.12,0:41:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,确保你和俄罗斯人相安无事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Make sure you're good with the Russkis.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.66,0:41:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能会需要我 我知道楚伊是这样\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Hey, you might need me. I know Chewy does.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.26,0:41:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,随便你怎么想吧 混蛋\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Whatever you need to tell yourself, cabrón.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.86,0:41:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(192,275)\fs18\bord1.5\shad0\fn方正黑体_GBK\b1}退后
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.41,0:41:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,乔治 叫医生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}George, call a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.65,0:41:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天啊 詹姆斯 你出什么事了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}My God, James. What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.47,0:41:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来找你了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}They're coming for you.
